text: A Major Leap For Drug Development? How BullFrog's AI Platform Is Driving Research Forward 7 minutes ago Vin Singh, Founder & CEO of BullFrog AI, was recently interviewed by Benzinga. BullFrog AI is a technology company offering its bfLEAP platform, transforming the field of precision medicine. The platform applies predictive analytics to all stages of drug development to create novel therapies faster – potentially revolutionizing drug development. The company has partnered with one of the most prestigious research institutions in the world, Johns Hopkins University, to license its AI technology.
